$$\begin{aligned}
& =\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{6}} \sqrt{2 \cos ^{2} \frac{3}{2} x} d x=\sqrt{2} \int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{6}}\left|\cos \frac{3}{2} x\right| d x \\
