19) $A=\left(\begin{array}{ll}3 & 1 \\ 2 & 2\end{array}\right)$ 의 고유치는 4,1 이며 각각에 대응하는 고유벡터 는 $\binom{1}{1},\binom{-1}{2}$ 이다.
$$\begin{aligned}
\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty}\left(\frac{1}{4} A\right)^{n} & =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{4^{n}} A^{n}=\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{4^{n}} P D^{n} P^{-1} \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{4^{n}}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -1 \\
1 & 2
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{cc}
4^{n} & 0 \\
0 & 1
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -1 \\
1 & 2
\end{array}\right)^{-1} \\
& =\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -1 \\
1 & 2
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & 0 \\
0 & \frac{1}{4^{n}}
\end{array}\right) \frac{1}{3}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
2 & 1 \\
-1 & 1
\end{array}\right) \\
& =\frac{1}{3}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -1 \\
1 & 2
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ll}
1 & 0 \\
0 & 0
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{rr}
2 & 1 \\
-1 & 1
\end{array}\right)=\frac{1}{3}\left(\begin{array}{ll}
2 & 1 \\
2 & 1
\end{array}\right)
\end{aligned}$$

이므로 $\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty}\left(\frac{1}{4} A\right)^{n} X=\binom{0}{0} \Leftrightarrow=\frac{1}{3}\left(\begin{array}{ll}2 & 1 \\ 2 & 1\end{array}\right)\binom{a}{b}=\binom{0}{0}$ 을 만족해야 한다.

따라서 보기 중 조건을 만족하는 경우는 $\binom{1}{-2}$ 이다.

정답: (5)

9) $\left(\begin{array}{ll}1 & 2 \\ 1 & 1 \\ 2 & 3\end{array}\right)\binom{x_{1}}{x_{2}}=\left(\begin{array}{l}3 \\ 1 \\ 3\end{array}\right) \Leftrightarrow A X=B$ 일 때, 최소제곱해는 다음과 같다.
$$\begin{aligned}
& \left(\begin{array}{lll}
1 & 1 & 2 \\
2 & 1 & 3
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{ll}
1 & 2 \\
1 & 1 \\
2 & 3
\end{array}\right)\binom{\overline{x_{1}}}{\overline{x_{2}}}=\left(\begin{array}{lll}
1 & 1 & 2 \\
2 & 1 & 3
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{l}
3 \\
1 \\
3
\end{array}\right) \\
& \Leftrightarrow\left(\begin{array}{cc}
6 & 9 \\
9 & 14
\end{array}\right)\left(\overline{\overline{x_{1}}} \overline{\overline{x_{2}}}\right)=\binom{10}{16}
\end{aligned}$$
$$\Leftrightarrow\left(\overline{\overline{x_{1}}}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
6 & 9 \\
9 & 14
\end{array}\right)^{-1}\binom{10}{16}=\frac{1}{3}\left(\begin{array}{cc}
14 & -9 \\
-9 & 6
\end{array}\right)\binom{10}{16}=\binom{-\frac{4}{3}}{2}$$

정답: (1)

